  <brief_title>Single Bundle Anterior Cruciate Ligament Reconstruction in Active Young Men</brief_title>
  <official_title>Single Bundle Anterior Cruciate Ligament Reconstruction in Active Young Men: Free Tendon Achilles Allograft vs. Bone-tendon Achilles Allograft</official_title>
